Description:
Photograph of a painting or drawing (15th of 16th century). Annotation on the back (not by Evers): "Boerner, Versteigerung 207 / Allegorische Zeichnung [...] Trautscholdt 19.4.43".

It possibly was originally part of Kiste 2 - Lose Akte 1 or of Karton - Lose Akte 7 (see RA 010 / 188 and RA 010 / 173).
